Detailed Description

Class that represent a cell in the OldMapHashTable.

The cell has functionality for finding an item at a specific location. Supports functions for selecting one, several or all types of items in the answer.

Do not use the OldMapHashTable directly, use the functions in OldGenericMap.

Is not completely thread safe yet. The allowed item types are stored in the HashTable. Also bboxes and GfxDataFull.
